{{Shield}}
== Overview ==
The Argon Array is another upgrade to the standard [[Argon (Shield)|Argon shield]]. The projectors have been altered to boost the recharge of the shield layer.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Argon Array can be bought in the workshop, or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
